Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.11,0:03:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿  这儿不能进来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, this area's restricted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.12,0:04:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨  你好  是他们通知我来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hi. Yeah, I know. They called me down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.62,0:04:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我来检查线路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Some of this wiring got screwed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.50,0:04:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么没人通知我  给我看一下单据\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nobody called it down to me. I'm gonna have to see a work order.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.00,0:04:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  请稍等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah. Just a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.30,0:04:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.97,0:04:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自找的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nothing personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.22,0:04:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就到这儿吧  诸位辛苦了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, I guess that wraps it up. Good work, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.98,0:04:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马提  我认为你这计划很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Marty, I couldn't be happier with the way this worked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.98,0:04:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衷心祝贺你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.07,0:04:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别关\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hold that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.70,0:04:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你支持\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Gee, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.92,0:04:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢你帮忙  鲍布\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thanks for pushing that, Bob. The light's on,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.55,0:04:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过要是指示灯坏了也说不定呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but you never know, it might be broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.38,0:04:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别胡说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.07,0:05:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗  亲爱的  今天会上...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Remember, honey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的天  鲍布  你按了什么钮?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jesus. Bob, what button did you push?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.12,0:06:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这幢楼里其它电梯是不是都停止使用了?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr Bagwell, make sure these other elevators remain locked down and empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.79,0:06:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了维修窗  现在没有任何地方可以进入电梯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's no doors, no other way in or out, except through access panels, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.46,0:06:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在有十三位乘客被困在电梯里  在三十层不到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What we have here are 13 passengers in an express elevator below floor 30.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.30,0:07:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缆绳被炸断了  案犯向我们提出要三百万元的赎金\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bomb's taken out cables. Bomber wants $3 million or he blows the brakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.34,0:07:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 给多少时间?  - 就一个小时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What's our clock? - He gave one hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.31,0:07:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可现在只剩下二十三分钟了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That leaves us 23 minutes exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.73,0:07:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让电梯再坠落下去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Anything to keep this elevator from falling?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.94,0:07:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,底层\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.15,0:07:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当局要防止惨剧发生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'd like to avoid that, Traven.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 要想办法把人救出来  - 那可是架高速电梯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- We can't unload the passengers? - This is an express elevator.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.69,0:07:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案犯把炸药安装在启动闸上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The only way in is through access panels. The bomber's wired the hatch,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.82,0:07:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他随时都可以让电梯坠落\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which seats him in the "crazy but not stupid" section.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.07,0:07:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里要求到现场去看一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sir, Harry volunteers to examine the device.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.54,0:07:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 没错  - 好吧  你们俩一起去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Yeah, right. - Fine. The two of you check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.50,0:07:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离电梯最近的维修窗在第三十二层\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The nearest access panel's on the 32nd floor in the lobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.59,0:07:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸清情况  不许擅自行动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I want reports only. We're in a holding pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.05,0:07:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃西  比格  你们两个去守住大门\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Worthy, Briggs, secure the base area.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.42,0:07:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人  尽快把楼里人疏散出去  快行动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Everyone else, I want you to affirm building evac. Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.59,0:07:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爬楼吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Looks like we're walkin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.85,0:07:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 快点  快点  留神脚下  - 二十九\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Hurry, but watch your step! - 29.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.02,0:07:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底下大厅  快一点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All the way down to the lobby! Let's go, folks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.69,0:07:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三十\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}30.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.36,0:08:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三十一\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}31.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.86,0:08:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三十二\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}32.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.05,0:08:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.72,0:08:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 快让我们出去  - 喂  喂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Come on! Get us outta here! - Hello! Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.26,0:09:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来人  快来人  让我们出去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Help! Please, get us out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.59,0:09:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来人啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.20,0:09:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来人  让我们出去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please! Get us out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.46,0:09:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面有人吗?  有人吗?  这是怎么了?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who's up there? Who's up there? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.38,0:09:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女士们  先生们  我们是警察\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ladies and gentlemen, this is the LAPD.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.84,0:09:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 谢天谢地  - 你们来干什么?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Thank God. - What are you doing up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.30,0:09:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这架电梯出了点故障  大家别紧张\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's been an elevator malfunction, so just relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.64,0:09:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点  快点想想办法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, come on! What are you guys waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.35,0:10:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别急  你们很快能出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll have you out of there as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我骗人?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Am I lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.48,0:10:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛派警察来?  警察会修电梯?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How come they sent cops here? Shouldn't they send repair guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.33,0:10:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么想?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.83,0:10:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 听你的  你是专家  - 干得很巧妙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You're the expert. I just work here. - Looks pretty solid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.21,0:10:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 像谁干的?  - 不知道  可准是个老手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Anyone we know? - I don't recognise the work, but he's a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.34,0:10:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 时间不多了  - 真急人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- He's cutting it close. - I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.51,0:10:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急也没用  麦克让等只好等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, what's to like? Mac said we hold, so we hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,临时测试  机场  案犯挟持一名人质朝前跑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right, pop quiz. The airport. Gunman with one hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.36,0:10:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼看要到机舱口\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's using her for cover. He's almost to a plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.74,0:10:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在百米之外\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're 100 feet away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.62,0:11:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.75,0:11:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打伤人质\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Shoot the hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.29,0:11:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么?  - 先朝人质开枪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What? - Take her out of the equation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把人质打伤再瞄准案犯  就这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Go for the good wound and he can't get to the plane with her. Clear shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.43,0:11:17.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真亏你想得出来  朝人质开枪  哼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're deeply nuts, you know that? "Shoot the hostage. "
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.23,0:11:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点不对劲  他打算炸电梯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Harry, this is wrong. He's gonna blow it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.65,0:11:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 怎么知道?  - 只是凭直觉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Why? - I don't know. Gut feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.48,0:11:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了  等着麦克下命令  沉住气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Right now Mac outranks your gut, so we sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.24,0:11:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么还没有修好?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is taking way too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.82,0:11:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这电梯重量多少?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How much d'you think that elevator weighs?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰克  得了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jack, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.33,0:11:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个主意  也许有点用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe we can do something about those hostages.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.33,0:11:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想朝人质开枪?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're not gonna shoot 'em, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.13,0:11:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨  去哪儿?  这是怎么了?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, where you going? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.84,0:11:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别走  别离开我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't go! Don't leave us here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.45,0:12:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我想帮他们摆脱困境\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, we just take them out of the equation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.15,0:12:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 能行吗?  - 可以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Are you sure it'll hold? - It'll hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.65,0:12:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Six minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.82,0:13:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再这么拖下去了  他又不答话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't get any more time. He's not talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.32,0:13:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快把赎金送过来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I need the goddamn money now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.67,0:13:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说说  哈里  我这是图个什么?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tell me again, Harry. Why did I take this job?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.09,0:13:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,图个退休之后能领那点养老金和一块镀金表\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, come on. 30 more years of this, you get a tiny pension and a cheap gold watch.
