Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.25,0:25:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个混蛋给炸死了  电梯里的人都没事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We got the bad guy and we didn't lose any civilians.
