Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.48,0:26:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里  我是说  我们赢了他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Harry, come on, man. I mean, we won. We got him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.94,0:26:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是没听?  还是怎么了?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you listen? Do you ever?
