Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.45,0:26:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能光凭直觉  否则会送命的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Guts'll get you so far, and then they'll get you killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.54,0:26:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好运不会老跟着你的  对吧  头儿?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Luck runs out sooner or later. Right, Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.63,0:26:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's right.
