Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.85,0:27:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  闹了一宵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't remember that well.
