Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.27,0:27:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?  记得我有次闹一宵  醒来有了老婆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah? The last time I partied like that, I woke up married, huh, Vinnie?
