Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.78,0:27:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.42,0:27:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明儿见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.37,0:29:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  杰克?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What do you think, Jack?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.46,0:29:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不去把司机的牙捡出来  再得一枚勋章?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You think if you pick up all the bus driver's teeth, they'll give you another medal?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.46,0:29:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天呐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.55,0:29:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当好我对付是吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You think I wouldn't have been prepared?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.21,0:29:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次电梯的事我准备了整整两年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Two years I spent setting up that elevatorjob.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.63,0:29:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把我的一切都投了进去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Two years I invested myself in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.80,0:29:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想象不出  我耗费了多少心血\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You couldn't understand the kind of commitment that I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.02,0:29:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等于毁了我一生  你以为我会这么轻易地放过你?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You ruined a man's life's work and you think you can walk away?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.35,0:29:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别做梦了  我引起你的重视了  对吗  杰克?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You got blinders on to the world, but I got your attention now, didn't I, Jack?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.57,0:29:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你干嘛不冲我来呢?  - 为了我自己  为了我的钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Why didn't you just come after me? - This is about me. This is about my money.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.40,0:29:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们欠我一大笔债  我得讨回来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is about money due me, which I will collect.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.49,0:29:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一共是三百七十万美金\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}$3.7 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.16,0:29:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我这把年纪的人  杰克  得为将来做打算\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's my nest egg, Jack. At my age, you gotta think ahead.
