Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.51,0:30:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再降到五十英里  就会爆炸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If it drops below 50, it blows up.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.10,0:30:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么办?  你怎么办?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What do you do? What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.02,0:30:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你说的是哪辆巴士?  - 你认为我会告诉你吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I'd wanna know what bus it was. - You think I'm gonna tell you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.86,0:30:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 是的  - 这很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Yes. - Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.19,0:30:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有几条游戏规则  杰克  你必须完全照办\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There are rules, Jack, and I want you to get this right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.69,0:30:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许乘客离开汽车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No one goes off the bus.
