Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.04,0:30:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 这点时间怕来不及  - 注意听  杰克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- We can't pull that kind of money in time. - Focus, Jack!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.71,0:30:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要管那辆车  车上没有电话  无线电坏了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your concern is the bus. And don't try to call. The radio's down.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.42,0:30:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那辆车牌号是二五二五  正从洛杉矶西区开往北区\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, the number of the bus is 2525. It's running downtown from Venice.
