Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.39,0:55:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这绝对不行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We can't do it, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.56,0:55:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没工夫看你表演特技了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's no time for any stunts.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.48,0:55:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得尽快让他们脱离困境\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We gotta get these people out of harm's way.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.56,0:55:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可他不允许  他一直在监视着我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I got orders. We move these people, he'll see.
