Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.95,0:56:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  哈里正在想办法查他  可能是个警察\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Harry's trying to find out who this guy is. We think maybe he's a cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.45,0:56:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警长  是他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lieutenant, it's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.25,0:56:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 他想找杰克  - 是他打来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- He wants to talk to Jack. - He's on the line for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.75,0:56:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 把号码告诉他  - 给他号码\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- OK, give him the number. - Give him the number.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.30,0:56:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 他怎么样?  - 血不太流了  可...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- How's he doing? - The bleeding is less, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.80,0:56:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 他们会救我们吗?  - 会的  他们是警察\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Are they going to help us? - Sure they are. They're the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.51,0:56:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠我们交的税发薪水  当然不希望我们死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, your taxes are paying their salary. If we die, they gotta take a pay cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.15,0:56:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意思  是说...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I mean, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.19,0:56:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.36,0:56:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来很信任你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think we have trust,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.95,0:56:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是从电视上看来  好像你打算让乘客离开巴士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but it looks on TV like you're trying to get those passengers off.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.28,0:56:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 有一个必须下车  - 可我们有约在先\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Look, you've gotta let me have one. - We went over the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.79,0:56:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况紧急\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As an act of faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.87,0:56:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客车司机被人开枪打伤了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have an injured man here. The driver's been shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.79,0:56:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰克  是不是你又想朝人质开枪了?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tell me you haven't been shooting the passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.63,0:57:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想警察一般不朝好人开枪  就该朝那些坏人开枪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I thought it was customary for a police officer to shoot the bad guys.
