Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.55,0:57:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要发点善心  可以早点拿到赎金\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It'll grease the wheels with the money men.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.47,0:57:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说还剩不少人质\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's still gonna be plenty of us to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.85,0:57:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧   孩子  你想法让司机下车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}OK, son, you can try and unload the driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.06,0:57:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你告诉那开车的野猫  千万别把车的速度放慢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You tell that wildcat behind the wheel not to slow down, though,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.48,0:57:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则不等他出去就会炸死  还有  杰克  你别想溜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}or he won't even get a chance to bleed to death. And, Jack, don't slip.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.53,0:57:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你说司机可以离开  - 诺沃  再靠近一点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- He's letting us unload the driver. - Norwood! Get us closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.24,0:57:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 杰克要把司机送到这车上  - 就送他?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- We're gonna get the driver off. - Just him?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.66,0:57:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 是的  大个儿  - 奥蒂斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- For now. Gigantor. - Ortiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.00,0:57:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥蒂斯  帮一下忙  好的  你把他递给我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ortiz, we're gonna need your help. I need you to pass him to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.04,0:57:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得小心点别把伤口弄出血了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Keep him straight, or the wound'll tear.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.51,0:57:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 让我们也过去  - 嘿  女士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What about the rest of us? - Hey, hey, hey! Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.01,0:57:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们也过去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't stay!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.35,0:57:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 怎么样?  - 不过挨了一枪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- How are you feeling? - Like I've been shot.
