Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.20,0:58:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠近  再近点  安妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Closer. A little closer, Annie.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.41,0:58:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 安妮  再近点  - 好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Annie, a little closer. - OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.71,0:58:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}OK, how's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.88,0:58:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sorry. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.13,0:58:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安妮  没关系  你再来试一次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}OK, Annie. No problem. Let's try it one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.76,0:58:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再近点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.39,0:58:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  好的  就这样  保持距离\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}OK! OK! Right there! Steady! Hold it steady!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.81,0:58:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉住了?  拉住了?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You got him? You got him?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.23,0:58:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm all right. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.74,0:58:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 上帝  - 太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Oh, my God. - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.91,0:59:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会好起来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's gonna be OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.79,0:59:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快  你把手伸给我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come on! Come on, lady. Give me your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.17,0:59:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我走了  安妮  - 不  海伦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I have to, Annie. - No, Helen!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.01,0:59:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 不  海伦  -  快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- No, Helen, no! - Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.30,0:59:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海伦  别过去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Helen, no! No!
