Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.64,0:59:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  海伦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, Helen!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.54,0:59:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈的  麦克  赶快把该死的直升飞机调走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Goddamn it, Mac! Get those fucking choppers outta here!
