Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.33,0:59:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才发生爆炸  但范围不是很大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}An explosion. Some kind of an explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.30,0:59:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  汽车没有爆炸  不过...  我的天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The bus hasn't exploded, but... Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.47,0:59:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人被炸出车外  还被钩在车底下  真是太可怕了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A woman caught in the blast fell. She was pulled under the wheels. This is terrible.
