Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.08,1:00:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不该来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.71,1:00:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不该  真的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't, you know...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.38,1:00:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不该上这车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is the wrong bus.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.92,1:00:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不该\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I mean, for me to...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.84,1:00:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不该这么死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't die here.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.89,1:00:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨  你闭嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, shut up, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.18,1:00:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我还有老婆呢  - 是吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I got a wife. - Oh, you do?
