Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.69,1:00:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这人废话太多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The guy's just talking crazy.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.03,1:00:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听了都心烦  现在谁心里都烦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He gets on my nerves. He gets on everybody's nerves.
