Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.70,1:01:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭你个儿大想欺负人  是不是?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, so you're a really tough guy, huh? Why don't we just step outside?
